parameters: All this water... Is this the sea?
Not the sea of stars, but the actual ocean?
All the rocks stacked up on each other
After I lost you in the Sea of Parlates,
I found myself in a place like this, and...
...Peh, don't go acting like you like me that much.
Do you hate being without me that badly?
I don't want it to happen ever again.
Who would've thought being so popular
The same as the ones from Talvirar,
Ugh, and we just stepped foot
We have to take care of them!
Don't make a fuss about these small fry.
Thou must be Ino and Fiede.
I have heard of your efforts.
Then you must be the Lord of Reason...?
So you came by to help us?
However, one only hunted down the Dark.
Helping thee was never one's intention.
Even still, thank you for your help.
If the Darkness monsters appeared here,
Do not get involved with this matter.
Thine purpose is this, is it not?
...Then, make sure thee act only in necessity.
One is bothered by the uncertain.
Of course. I feel for Miss Kilma,
but our purpose is to enjoy this trip.
Besides... I still fear for those
Even if she says not to get involved...
